des: "This is the fruit dip that Farmer Jack puts in with your fruit tray when you order it in the deli.  Its creamy and delicious and i always have to make an extra batch...quick and easy to make."
ins: Mix the yogurt and whipped topping together in a large bowl. Stir in the strawberry gelatin and the sugar. Mix until well dissolved. If a richer taste is desired, whisk in the strawberry flavored cream cheese until smooth. Garnish with fresh strawberries.
